headline: Northern Trust Pension Universe Data: Canadian Pension Plans Generated Positive Q1 Returns in Turbulent Markets
summary: TORONTO, May 01, 2025--The median Canadian pension plan gained 1.5% in a volatile first quarter of 2025, according to the Northern Trust Canada Universe.
